doc.body:
This hook is [SWR powered](https://docs.reservoir.tools/docs/hooks#swr-powered-hooks) and also handles [infinite loading UX](https://docs.reservoir.tools/docs/hooks#infinite-loading-hooks). Use this hook to fetch token details, using the [Tokens](ref:gettokensv5) endpoint. It takes a query parameter which maps to the same parameters that the api endpoint uses.
[block:code]
{
  "codes": [
    {
      "code": "import { useTokens } from '@reservoir0x/reservoir-kit-ui'\n\nconst { data: tokens } = useTokens({\n  tokens: [\"0xb47e3cd837ddf8e4c57f05d70ab865de6e193bbb:1\"],\n})",
      "language": "typescript"
    }
  ]
}
[/block]
